{"title":"UTD. Evaluación y manejo de la primera convulsión en adulto-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/UTD. Evaluación y manejo de la primera convulsión en adulto-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Evaluación y manejo de la\\Nprimera convulsión en adulto","guid":"ngCdDXbCDv_nsZ67s2DvoQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación y manejo de la\\Nprimera crisis en adultos","guid":"C-zoRLfPAT7FOO4Es3lhCA","children":[]},{"id":"2","parent":"0","text":"1. DEFINICIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"1.1. Crisis epiléptica","guid":"czJMAxi0NR62e9OgYh188w","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"▪ Cambio repentino en el comportamiento\\N→ hipersincronización eléctrica neuronal\\Nen la corteza cerebral","guid":"tDorapP2yuNUR3pxLLPd6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"1.2. Crisis sintomática\\Naguda (provocada)","guid":"Ic6CqAatJdWvZb5b7L_YqQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"▪ Crisis asociada temporalmente a una\\Nagresión sistémica o cerebral","guid":"BZxv-fUDBsmC61zhqD8tPg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"▪ Ejemplos de\\Nagresiones:","guid":"xOb3lLsrFz6vEBB_Wrth2A","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Trastornos metabólicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Abstinencia de\\Ndrogas/alcohol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• ACV, encefalitis,\\NTEC agudo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"5","text":"Criterios temporales\\N(recomendación de consenso)","guid":"TYceq3tq1j9MDMWHzAjJbw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"▪ ≤1 semana de ACV, TEC,\\Nencefalopatía anóxica, cx intracraneal","guid":"UDwPv7xhqYMNG-4JxGYGWQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"▪ Identificación inicial de\\Nhematoma subdural","guid":"e7Cle5QXLoPCa9SrUJCcKQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"▪ Fase activa de\\Ninfección SNC","guid":"fy2oG9d30IWTHs8rbEZI5g","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"▪ ≤24 h de alteración\\Nmetabólica grave","guid":"GgtSAhJ4sSfSV1Y5vc6I0A","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"5","text":"Datos epidemiológicos","guid":"5ObjesKrrb9KAoV50eRfEg","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"▪ Hasta 40% de las primeras crisis\\Nson sintomáticas agudas","guid":"7Q2UHAkS6vyCaKmp9qnaww","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"▪ Poca probabilidad de\\Nprogresar a epilepsia","guid":"vStiFbLpYmYanlKXJ4KRzw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"▪ Puede evolucionar a crisis\\Nsintomáticas remotas o epilepsia\\N(post-ACV, hemorragia, TEC)","guid":"3SjpGG5Bkbm76LR7BTZjvQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"2","text":"1.3. Crisis no provocada","guid":"eKOk8P9NbFYXfwTe57RnoA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"▪ Etiología desconocida o asociada a\\Nlesión cerebral preexistente o\\Nenfermedad progresiva del SNC","guid":"QUGRJBzTapXXt1BNRWwr7A","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"▪ También llamadas “crisis\\Nsintomáticas remotas”","guid":"P7JM27SyJviACK501wm_og","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"▪ Mayor riesgo de epilepsia futura que\\Nlas crisis sintomáticas agudas","guid":"Me3E8Q42aNB_fSIFCjQWug","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"2","text":"1.4. Epilepsia","guid":"knW9eRuhpbSUBLNHSuxJPA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"▪ Definición (ILAE 2014) → al\\Nmenos uno de los siguientes:","guid":"Ag4xIWUbmSb_1ZR49F5GJQ","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• ≥2 crisis no provocadas\\Nseparadas por >24 h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• 1 crisis no provocada + riesgo de\\Nrecurrencia similar al de 2 crisis\\N(≥60% en 10 años)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Diagnóstico de\\Nsíndrome epiléptico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"▪ Importancia de neuroimagen y EEG en primera\\Ncrisis → algunos pacientes cumplen criterios de\\Nepilepsia desde la primera crisis","guid":"1nwe4u5LmKbeAoZU3FWnHQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"24","text":"▪ “Trastorno convulsivo” =\\N“Epilepsia” (ILAE)","guid":"QCx5xu4nuwEfnS-X3SqV8A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"2. EPIDEMIOLOGÍA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"▪ Crisis epilépticas: 8-10% de\\Nla población en la vida","guid":"9yTeGKIFsLtFzLOqz9SNyQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"▪ 1-2% de visitas\\Na urgencias","guid":"USAirLT61zu4NTVNJqpSng","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"▪ 25% de las crisis en\\Nurgencias son la primera crisis","guid":"iFZPh8siZcY5d8DUiBnarQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"3. DIAGNÓSTICO\\NDIFERENCIAL","guid":"PIl7EPK74L8yMVm3SXaEdA","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Eventos paroxísticos\\Nno epilépticos","guid":"t8YzM8IcnlNzl9fpGmimVQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"▪ Síncope /\\Nsíncope\\Nconvulsivo","guid":"J6tHyL6nSI7Pd-wdPw3a3g","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"▪ Migraña","guid":"KVf12tKDaAjl7p9J4aHPBA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"▪ AIT","guid":"RNIvojicmDp_143qwx1Sqg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"▪ Crisis psicógenas\\Nno epilépticas","guid":"XnrfYZqzr-82MRtHFiUe7g","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"Estados epilépticos (pueden ser\\Nprimera manifestación de crisis)","guid":"fvBJnGo395YQXZefzjQ-lA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"▪ Estado\\Nepiléptico\\Nconvulsivo","guid":"VIlfB2h0afP7AvtS_B277Q","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"▪ Estado epiléptico\\Nno convulsivo","guid":"esfYAgIO-IcgA3L91UbCFw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"Causas de crisis\\Nepilépticas y epilepsia","guid":"p2mG-3tFMoRCDveB9CDLQw","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"1. Clasificación\\Nde las causas","guid":"tuJhkb5fwlPJZBXnKON7Ag","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"▪ Según contexto → Sintomática aguda\\N(provocada) vs. No provocada","guid":"Quf66oCsEtHr4SQoLQjyqw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"▪ Según tipo → Focal\\Nvs. Generalizada","guid":"knU2l2z0OVgwGKcNVZT2FQ","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"▪ Diferencias por edad","guid":"6G03umZ-doGR2nyzN-odow","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Adultos mayores con primera crisis → ↑\\NProbabilidad de identificar causa con\\Nevaluación inicial + neuroimagen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Epilepsia en niños/adolescentes →\\NFrecuente origen genético/metabólico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Epilepsia en adultos → Mayor frecuencia\\Nde causas adquiridas (vasculares,\\Nneurodegenerativas, neoplásicas)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"44","text":"2. Causas de crisis\\Nsintomáticas agudas","guid":"CDVCUWbBFv8uJYIKkArrjA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"2.1. Lesión\\Ncerebral aguda","guid":"IlTiAeoGHHcUBXwDr8ob1Q","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"(Cualquier insulto agudo al\\Ncerebro puede causar crisis)","guid":"DTihJJCtv7UKutbpOsUPiQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"▪ Enfermedades\\Ncerebrovasculares","guid":"Ko9odv6ZPnhUcS5M2d_p8A","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• ACV isquémico/hemorrágico\\N(especialmente hemorragia lobar)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"• Hematoma subdural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"• Hemorragia\\Nsubaracnoidea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"• Trombosis\\Nvenosa cerebral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"• PRES (síndrome de\\Nencefalopatía posterior\\Nreversible)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"53","text":"▪ TEC agudo","guid":"Ov9rH5LiG9Av_pPW8tv1zg","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Leve:\\NConmoción\\Ncerebral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• Moderado-severo:\\NMayor riesgo de crisis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"53","text":"▪ Eclampsia","guid":"hlmG8r_W1DDKM0QO3eXGtA","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Crisis tónico-clónicas\\Ngeneralizadas → Último\\Ntrimestre o postparto inmediato","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"53","text":"▪ Hipoxia-isquemia","guid":"Jr7YX384H8xhYrb06sfV8A","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Encefalopatía\\Nhipóxico-isquémica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"53","text":"▪ Infecciones del SNC","guid":"VWs4O5K2RBXMSb4xPAyOdA","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Absceso cerebral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Meningitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• Encefalitis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"52","text":"2.2. Enfermedades\\Nsistémicas agudas","guid":"d2mvb6m5JQttq6Q37j0qSg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"▪ Alteraciones\\Nmetabólicas","guid":"FZLvMwrsi8UGWCzmVA3BCw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Hipoglucemia → Riesgo alto en DM\\Ntratado con insulina/orales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Hiperglucemia no cetósica →\\NCrisis motoras focales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Hiponatremia → Descenso brusco\\N→ Crisis tónico-clónicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• Hipocalcemia → Rara; post-tiroidectomía,\\Nhipoparatiroidismo, insuf. renal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"• Hipomagnesemia → Irritabilidad,\\Nconfusión, mioclonías, tetania","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"• Uremia → Crisis mioclónicas y\\Ntónico-clónicas (10% IRC avanzada)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"73","text":"• Hipertiroidismo → Puede inducir o\\Nagravar crisis epilépticas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"72","text":"▪ Trastornos del\\Nmetabolismo de\\Nporfirinas","guid":"1WTiUVmQvo0QiyP9LZa6Aw","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Porfiria intermitente aguda →\\NCrisis + dolor abdominal +\\Ncambios conductuales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"72","text":"▪ Sustancias y\\Nabstinencia","guid":"14E6EdGMC-LMaXLlYWWLeg","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"• Abstinencia → Alcohol (7-48 h post\\Núltima ingesta), benzodiacepinas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"• Drogas → Cocaína, anfetaminas, PCP,\\Nintoxicación medicamentosa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"3. Causas de crisis no\\Nprovocadas y epilepsia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"3.1. Lesiones\\Ncerebrales\\Nestructurales","guid":"mapuv0aKZX8dMj76sJRPeQ","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"▪ Epilepsia del lóbulo\\Ntemporal mesial","guid":"ZAO4P7CK1mD76X81WEw-dw","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"•  80% inicia en adolescencia (pero\\Npuede debutar en adultez joven)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"▪ Enfermedades\\Ncerebrovasculares","guid":"DqIGJCHAxi8KqKy8e7ij9w","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• ACV previo →\\NEpilepsia post-ACV","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"▪ Tumores\\Nprimarios/metástasis","guid":"HRxYa886WFzcs7rVyPXULg","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Gliomas, meningiomas,\\Nmetástasis cerebrales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"87","text":"▪\\NMalformaciones\\Nvasculares","guid":"UHiFJ4b8mtipGLESj9gMZg","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"• Cavernomas,\\Nmalformaciones\\Narteriovenosas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"87","text":"▪ Infecciones\\Nprevias del SNC","guid":"OKsm9W8wsol39d8NRbV5EQ","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Neurocisticercosis (causa\\Nfrecuente en zonas endémicas)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"87","text":"▪ TEC previo","guid":"kVmfLAxfKeobMIpDAJO01g","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Epilepsia postraumática","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"87","text":"▪ Enfermedades\\Nneurodegenerativas","guid":"PveAH__SN84g8k6vl6GQ-w","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Alzheimer → Aumento\\Ndel riesgo de crisis","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"86","text":"3.2. Epilepsias\\Ngeneralizadas","guid":"2tPsyTfqOaDLRw84pJQWPQ","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"▪ Síndromes\\Nepilépticos\\Nidiopáticos","guid":"WAyrT1kSQJGBvkKIC-WUGg","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Epilepsia mioclónica juvenil\\N(EMJ) → Mioclonías matutinas +\\Ncrisis generalizadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"• Epilepsia generalizada idiopática de\\Ninicio tardío (raro en adultos)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"0","text":"4. Frecuencia relativa\\Nde las causas","guid":"DZtG8QAjqQyENZ7QksaHWQ","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"▪ 60% de epilepsias →\\NEtiología desconocida incluso\\Ntras evaluación completa","guid":"cYiTdX-D_0rL96iq4Cu2gw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"▪ En adultos → Predominio de\\Ncausas adquiridas frente a\\Ngenéticas/metabólicas de la infancia","guid":"25xQzf5nB7zEps_89W3K4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"Tipos de crisis\\Nepilépticas","guid":"kUIeJp8XJwH_CgZLYqr6yg","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"1. Clasificación general","guid":"_wSmsRMKqVyfIQ4bYhIZ_A","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"▪ Focales → Inician en una región\\Nespecífica del cerebro","guid":"45KnTDfc1N5Kq3IPyP01yw","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"▪ Generalizadas → Afectan ambos\\Nhemisferios simultáneamente","guid":"ar0iNOqb53GmLfJPpuN8Vg","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"▪ Factores determinantes","guid":"tlLPIH0FnZH4ampkAX18uQ","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Localización cortical →\\NManifiesta síntomas específicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Extensión de la actividad → Puede\\Ncomprometer o no la conciencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"109","text":"2. Crisis focales","guid":"UHgfwHRFRTvLDKkhtAgSeQ","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"2.1. Crisis focales con conciencia\\Npreservada (focales simples)","guid":"MVFM3iXySVL7tU8QPmIsyA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"▪ Síntomas dependen de la\\Nlocalización cortical afectada","guid":"_MFYCSQdXoiY0IH9wFKFrA","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Lóbulo occipital →\\NLuces centelleantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Corteza motora → Movimientos\\Nrítmicos (crisis jacksoniana)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"• Lóbulo parietal → Alteraciones\\Nen percepción espacial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"• Lóbulo frontal dominante →\\NDificultades súbitas del habla","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"117","text":"▪ Aura → Corresponde a una crisis focal que\\Nno compromete la conciencia","guid":"QnG_RIdbHj-1KUu6Tk-2Lg","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"• Síntomas iniciales pueden\\Npasar desapercibidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"• En algunos casos, evoluciona\\Na crisis más extensas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"117","text":"▪ Período postictal","guid":"rnb1ftnF2ZDCU7KvgWZRFg","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Puede haber recuperación inmediata o\\Ndéficit neurológico transitorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Ejemplo: Parálisis de Todd (debilidad\\Npostictal en región afectada)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"116","text":"2.2. Crisis focales con alteración de la\\Nconciencia (focales complejas)","guid":"i8W1qSfTmps1tFWVKanPsg","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"▪ Más frecuentes en\\Nadultos con epilepsia","guid":"_JpYK46NDsQv8Rbsid-lUQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"▪\\NManifestaciones\\Nclínicas","guid":"dyxySsddYDeRYM87SjpwNg","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Paciente despierto\\Npero desconectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Mirada fija + movimientos\\Nautomáticos (gestos, masticación,\\Ndeglución, repetición de frases)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"• Puede presentar\\Nagitación si se le inmoviliza","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"129","text":"▪ Duración","guid":"8kMNYhlbpM64-8iKrzCM7w","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• <3 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"• Postictal: somnolencia,\\Nconfusión, cefalea (horas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"• Amnesia del evento","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"116","text":"2.3. Crisis focales con\\Ngeneralización secundaria","guid":"MZVnnGLfFg2yN0gs8ASU7Q","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"▪ Cualquier crisis focal puede progresar →\\NCrisis tónico-clónica bilateral","guid":"vJTUE1Tjo1lk9K0UShLFxA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"▪ Si propagación es lenta → Se\\Nidentifican síntomas focales previos","guid":"NH09jCOX-enKWhJ1qNJwwA","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"▪ Si propagación es rápida →\\NPuede parecer una crisis\\Ngeneralizada primaria","guid":"E6T4LKGXjBItqDccKadCvg","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"▪ Indicadores de\\Ninicio focal","guid":"lhVeS1eLxup_6aC-YfMUkg","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Aura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"• Déficit neurológico postictal\\N(ej. Parálisis de Todd)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"• Lesión estructural en\\Nneuroimagen o EEG focal","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"109","text":"3. Crisis generalizadas","guid":"bfrXCpH8axBmgoH3rUj_ww","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"▪ Poco frecuente en adultos\\Ncomo inicio primario","guid":"afcgvHN6Xyf1cVLZsHX7qw","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"▪ Síndromes epilépticos\\Ngenéticos pueden manifestarse\\Nen adolescencia o adultez","guid":"9j6bap-5wPm1j_WXUsDiDA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"3.1. Crisis tónico-clónicas\\Ngeneralizadas (“Gran Mal”)","guid":"lC28AqEW-3DX4H6Ebji_rw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"▪ Fases","guid":"YKLf7prq-lIMDxX8fEEETQ","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Tónica → Pérdida brusca de\\Nconciencia + rigidez muscular difusa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"• Clónica → Movimientos\\Nde sacudida rítmica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"• Postictal → Somnolencia\\Nprofunda, confusión, agitación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"150","text":"▪ Hallazgos comunes","guid":"xcS76OBGHI7ztmI41Xycew","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Grito inicial, cianosis, mordedura\\Nlingual, sialorrea espumosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"• Puede no haber recuerdo del aura si\\Nla propagación es rápida","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"147","text":"3.2. Crisis de\\Nausencia (“Petit\\NMal”)","guid":"eD0KDYkegJflyTPGFAY9FA","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"▪ Inicio en infancia →\\NDesconexión breve (5-10 seg)","guid":"drRx8q3BOW_TaOrqmFBymQ","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"▪ Características","guid":"WF0YgWxVoFFgt76ifWFKrg","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Interrupción de actividad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"• Mirada fija","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"160","text":"• Parpadeo,\\Nchasquidos\\Nlabiales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"160","text":"• Sin postictal evidente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"158","text":"▪ Ocurren en racimos →\\NHasta cientos al día","guid":"XklNKMLl55_ZsXkde4Y1Kw","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"147","text":"3.3. Crisis de\\Nausencia atípicas","guid":"fYZ4pJXt-P3e3rOu2MS1Yw","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"▪ Duración\\Nprolongada (>10\\Nseg)","guid":"XJuXR3IxpNAXwYKnZlVp0g","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"▪ Aparición y\\Nterminación más\\Nlenta","guid":"lt1wIiJ_fYxCXiItDiXWIA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"▪ Movimientos adicionales\\N(manos, labios) → Puede\\Nconfundirse con crisis focales","guid":"zWSWE4P1QBMKfD0hGCLOcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"147","text":"3.4. Otras crisis\\Ngeneralizadas","guid":"uW0ouG6XF66MSym3I38OrQ","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"▪ Clónicas → Sacudidas rítmicas\\N(brazos, cuello, cara)","guid":"_b5EPw9zUypUcOxFb40ohg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"▪ Mioclónicas → Sacudidas\\Nmusculares breves y bruscas\\N(usualmente en brazos)","guid":"dL7LcGwRFkVufxxsH6tDKQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"▪ Tónicas → Contracción muscular\\Nsostenida → Caída si afecta piernas","guid":"Af4qApIgQO-CvMnUdtwB-w","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"170","text":"▪ Atónicas (“Drop attacks”) →\\NPérdida súbita del tono\\Nmuscular → Caídas bruscas","guid":"UaNKkhnKm-NHiLn6u6ZQNA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"109","text":"4. Consideraciones\\Nfinales","guid":"v7aAYHa0c84TC9HTHBqQQQ","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"▪ Diferenciar crisis focal vs.\\Ngeneralizada es clave → Implica\\Ndiferencias en tratamiento y pronóstico","guid":"TNaXUkNW7p5y63z-7i2jYg","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"▪ Síndromes epilépticos generalizados →\\NSuelen iniciar en la infancia, pero algunos\\Nse presentan en adultez","guid":"OEzBa34Xved0zWZZuCV9Ng","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"▪ Neuroimagen y EEG → Fundamentales\\Npara diagnóstico y clasificación","guid":"GNuASvVhtLhWcX3P6aWZdw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación inicial de la\\Nprimera crisis epiléptica","guid":"o9070pnKZFOC0YWxzhRdeg","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"1. Objetivos de\\Nla evaluación","guid":"juLy-4tFMVLbQ3fBF9K93Q","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"▪ Confirmar si el evento fue una crisis\\Nepiléptica o un evento no epiléptico","guid":"pIKVAIWscIQckPGscQj_Ww","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"▪ Determinar si la crisis fue provocada\\N(sistémica o lesión cerebral aguda) o no\\Nprovocada (disfunción intrínseca del SNC)","guid":"0bUiQKZPy2mTOv_4_CTWLw","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"▪ Identificar patología cerebral subyacente\\Nsi la crisis fue no provocada","guid":"Lx4vSBAqfkIW_mezwn30nA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"▪ Estimar el riesgo\\Nde recurrencia","guid":"JEeVr061GtUrBYIh19gMVQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"🔹 Implicaciones → Decisión sobre\\Ninicio de tratamiento antiepiléptico y\\Nmanejo de causa subyacente","guid":"7B-wmxJ196qAWllF0YgZoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"179","text":"2. Diagnóstico de\\Ncrisis epiléptica","guid":"jsinpUABT7OCkjb3XwmEMA","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"▪ Principalmente clínico →\\NHistoria del evento +\\Ncaracterísticas del episodio","guid":"d2AhjiYw6cq1vtx4mnp3Pg","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"▪ Apoyo diagnóstico → Neuroimagen,\\NEEG y estudios de laboratorio cuando\\Nla etiología no es clara","guid":"tDquBlEkUyaXhptgl8lsew","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"▪ Características típicas","guid":"3NKy3Hy2vGB7kk6TPUvFsA","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Eventos episódicos,\\Nbreves y estereotipados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• Inicio brusco, progresión\\Nrápida en segundos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"• Resolución espontánea en <2-3 min\\N(más prolongados → considerar\\Ndiagnósticos alternativos)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"186","text":"🔹 Diferencial → Migraña aura\\N(progresión en 5-10 min), AIT, síncope\\Nconvulsivo, crisis psicógenas","guid":"2Fa3HuBuZx957xHvzXtiRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"179","text":"3. Historia clínica","guid":"WxFuS68gFToEjKZgM9-KCg","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"3.1. Descripción\\Ndel evento","guid":"mWUFBNx0io3It_05B20_rg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"▪ Datos clave","guid":"ZinbK4kgrUtVDmCKo3DFtw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Circunstancias previas\\N(desencadenantes, actividad previa)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Fases del evento → Inicio,\\Nmanifestaciones\\Nmotoras/sensoriales,\\Nprogresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"• Duración total","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"• Estado postictal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"195","text":"▪ Dificultades en\\Nla anamnesis","guid":"8jYNnnnPf1HqZU-02O_-EQ","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Pacientes con crisis focales sin\\Nalteración de conciencia →\\NPueden describir el evento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Crisis con alteración de\\Nconciencia o generalizadas →\\NRequieren relato de testigos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"195","text":"▪ Características útiles\\Npara localización","guid":"0KwN6m4zCRA9uBGsvTkGkw","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"• Giro de cabeza/desviación ocular →\\NLóbulo frontal contralateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"• Déficit sensitivo unilateral →\\NLóbulo parietal contralateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"• Alteración del lenguaje →\\NHemisferio dominante","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"208","parent":"194","text":"3.2. Periodo postictal","guid":"eBIeXqVmus6oIoXrpFE9aQ","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"▪ Definición → Fase de\\Nrecuperación tras la crisis","guid":"SbEjcjF4qfSvjaZ5p-Qeeg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"▪ Manifestaciones frecuentes → Confusión,\\Ndisminución del nivel de alerta","guid":"m8JOZXX42zGMGL5LE8UlQQ","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"208","text":"▪ Déficits neurológicos focales\\Ntransitorios (ej. Parálisis de Todd)","guid":"wEZv5Bl7eCpoyGSsAr2dVA","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Debilidad unilateral\\Npost-crisis focal motora","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Puede durar\\Nminutos a horas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"• Puede simular un AIT/ACV\\Nen presentación inicial","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"208","text":"▪ Duración variable","guid":"ojuVcqcRmP4gbEZlbeJPyA","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"• Adultos jóvenes con crisis\\Nfocales → Pocos segundos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"• Ancianos con crisis generalizadas\\N→ Horas o incluso días","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"208","text":"▪ Persistencia prolongada →\\NConsiderar estado epiléptico\\Nsubclínico (evaluar con EEG urgente)","guid":"HayANm5Eho2VNY8YSFJabg","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"194","text":"3.3.\\NDesencadenantes o\\Ngatillantes","guid":"HMF0_rtxfu8Th2ZRxPKZtw","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"▪ Estímulos específicos →\\NEmociones intensas, ejercicio,\\Nluces intermitentes","guid":"doj-xLkdHCfvOhVwksYBdQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"▪ Factores fisiológicos → Fiebre,\\Nmenstruación, privación de\\Nsueño, embarazo, estrés","guid":"UmDiOBegtxI0372-lLyAKw","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"▪ Desencadenantes sistémicos\\N→ Alteraciones metabólicas,\\Nabstinencia, fármacos","guid":"Mf9X0fIr_s3BYwH4KSkyhA","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"🔹 Importante → La mayoría de los\\Npacientes con epilepsia NO tienen un\\Ndesencadenante claro","guid":"HXUGVP9zw12ZKDC7rA_O7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"194","text":"3.4. Eventos\\Nprevios similares","guid":"8zPB66GkteMwTiZff1s5pw","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"▪ 20-60% de pacientes con\\N“primera crisis” han tenido\\Neventos previos no reconocidos","guid":"IBy5SuwJ0PpmqG9RjWFt-Q","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"▪ Ejemplos","guid":"af2sccIc6wwO-K4z9YjPRg","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Espasmos mioclónicos matutinos →\\NEpilepsia mioclónica juvenil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Crisis focales menores → Aura olfatoria,\\Ngustatoria, episodios de pánico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"194","text":"3.5. Medicación\\Ny sustancias","guid":"yo6VYDSeNB8YltXKP_yMNQ","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"▪ Fármacos con riesgo de crisis →\\NIntoxicación, sobredosis o\\Ninteracción con otros fármacos","guid":"nrX2G3-pKJSW0RxtuxvcJg","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"▪ Abstinencia → Alcohol,\\Nbenzodiazepinas","guid":"oXbVIe6-9G1BnABE0zevnQ","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"▪ Drogas ilícitas →\\NCocaína, anfetaminas","guid":"6-yT3HnAWMxYyXUxi0YQIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"194","text":"3.6. Antecedentes\\Npersonales y familiares","guid":"fxPAfjvGe3lMwqu2YLpknQ","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"▪ Factores de riesgo","guid":"U3ifwweGPBZaIj4vd0C5JA","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• TEC, infecciones previas del\\NSNC, ACV, Alzheimer","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"• Inmunosupresión, neoplasias, lupus,\\Nporfiria, anemia falciforme","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"▪ Historia familiar → Riesgo mayor si\\Nhay antecedentes de epilepsia","guid":"xH1goAXYfO7V87mmaFZH4g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"179","text":"4. Examen físico","guid":"sBmKux6MMffOkkbNzU-5lw","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"▪ General → Buscar signos de\\Ninfección, trauma oculto","guid":"FyKuaostQJGDlc2DAC9qeg","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"▪ Neurológico →","guid":"MfxVvtaHir_NuS25nL1hbQ","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"• Déficits focales →\\NPosible lesión estructural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"• Signos de Babinski/Hiperreflexia\\N→ Lesión contralateral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"238","text":"▪ Signos\\Nindirectos de\\Ncrisis","guid":"0XJV3Xn7PfJPI5EJ8Eh0eg","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Mordedura lingual (borde lateral → crisis\\Nepiléptica; punta → caída/trauma)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"243","text":"• Incontinencia urinaria\\N(poco específico)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"179","text":"5. Evaluación de\\Nlaboratorio","guid":"H6k8hd-CciuS6wOMg0e1Uw","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"5.1. Estudios básicos","guid":"sETVysEtNAsM3KfbFEwVXg","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"▪ Glicemia capilar\\N(todos los pacientes)","guid":"ZKGQK6nwq551ntj7RtZXqQ","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"▪ Electrolitos\\N(Na, Ca, Mg)","guid":"nM18RzAdphTMCnAqtew0DA","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"247","text":"▪ Lactato sérico (elevado\\Npost-crisis generalizada)","guid":"URW-hxdRIEz6zMKSwxudug","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"247","text":"▪ Hemograma, función\\Nrenal y hepática","guid":"S3ai9bBpexyJz8V4hTudiw","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"247","text":"▪ Uroanálisis","guid":"lv1DMY1vlvh4ii_Y0Hu_7A","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"247","text":"🔹 Toxicología → Si hay\\Nsospecha de intoxicación/drogas","guid":"Y7GkF9yBb6nDWaYYioo9-Q","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"247","text":"🔹 β-hCG →\\NMujeres en edad\\Nfértil","guid":"1T93l1D16WMPh2oegtBGpA","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"246","text":"5.2. Estudios con\\Nutilidad limitada","guid":"z02dwF74apr00eWAcfGL_A","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"▪ Prolactina sérica → Elevada\\Nen crisis tónico-clónica/focal,\\Npero no específica","guid":"nXbsIK90gbQ1pEyqzIMyaw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"179","text":"6. Electrocardiograma\\N(ECG)","guid":"Yv2Bkl2ksbAg3eywpw9CWA","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"▪ Obligatorio en toda pérdida\\Nde conciencia → Evaluar\\Nsíncope cardiogénico","guid":"15iYJURzEo6utoD-Uk3IyA","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"▪ Identificar arritmias (ej. QT largo\\Nadquirido/congénito, intoxicación por\\Nantidepresivos tricíclicos)","guid":"8dzxo8zf2XMXXK2Q6pMRjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"179","text":"7. Neuroimagen","guid":"4Tu5BmcXdD7T1Ncwz0Txog","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"7.1. Indicación","guid":"p01hjOSlWSeq_NbkkS2IAw","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"▪ TODOS los adultos\\Ncon primera crisis","guid":"DMEC2KIeVJ1WpwL6mq1mbw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"▪ Urgente → Déficit neurológico, estado mental\\Nalterado persistente, fiebre, TEC reciente, neoplasia,\\Ninmunosupresión, anticoagulación","guid":"BOs209jT2FAdsXY2g5QmKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"260","text":"7.2. Modalidad\\Nde imagen","guid":"4TA7AxlMhH56NxIhnlbt5g","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"▪ TAC sin contraste","guid":"NUvRW27DfAOdXy7mZ3xqMw","children":[{"id":"266","parent":"265","text":"• Primera elección en urgencias\\N→ Detecta hemorragia, infartos,\\Nlesiones expansivas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"265","text":"• Complementar con\\NMRI si normal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"264","text":"▪ Resonancia\\Nmagnética (MRI)","guid":"gF7UbxgeHsRhTXyalGaOiA","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Estudio de elección en evaluación\\Nambulatoria → Mayor sensibilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"264","text":"🔹 MRI\\Nprotocolo\\Nepilepsia","guid":"Dyln_AOLikg-HF3DPMFgdQ","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• T1 volumétrico 3D →\\NIdentificación de displasias\\Ncorticales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"• T2/FLAIR coronal → Hipocampo\\N(esclerosis mesial temporal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"• Gradient Echo →\\NMalformaciones vasculares","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"179","text":"8. Electroencefalograma\\N(EEG)","guid":"__ZqgFCzK-0A1_3L6bV6IQ","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"8.1. Indicaciones","guid":"aprR-3oileoMqtBQInEdoA","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"▪ EEG urgente → Si persiste alteración de\\Nconciencia post-crisis (>60 min) → Buscar\\Nactividad epiléptica subclínica","guid":"AftzkO71YVLmxUsnc1Jmcg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"▪ EEG ambulatorio →\\NPacientes recuperados →\\NEvaluar riesgo de recurrencia","guid":"8jpHPydKsRjXngFtn-7hQA","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"🔹 Datos útiles en EEG","guid":"EqmGj7-mYhqoSe1d2p_3Zg","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• Descargas epileptiformes → ↑\\NRiesgo de recurrencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"278","text":"• Slowing difuso → No específico\\N(encefalopatía, fármacos)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"179","text":"9. Punción lumbar","guid":"cJxpT4BeaiFLKeVM54tbdw","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"▪ Indicada solo si sospecha de infección\\NSNC o hemorragia subaracnoidea","guid":"VD1ZQu8z-L3hlprjEEpuSA","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"▪ Contraindicada antes de\\Nneuroimagen para descartar\\Nlesión ocupante de espacio","guid":"Dj1gMeu4BaAHTYwaW6q0Ow","children":[]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"179","text":"10. Resumen\\Nde abordaje","guid":"tRqBXJIIfMckit-I5Ul59A","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"1️⃣ Historia clínica detallada\\N(descripción del evento,\\Npostictal, factores de riesgo)","guid":"o_SbHikoZI22T3JAgi0gvw","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"284","text":"2️⃣ Examen físico dirigido (déficits focales,\\Nsignos de trauma, arritmias)","guid":"PNyhkYrLLZpvgdsCBLEdhw","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"284","text":"3️⃣ Laboratorio básico\\N(glicemia, electrolitos, lactato)","guid":"KXN4mCJ_Wrq6G1rbeWzjFA","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"284","text":"4️⃣ ECG (descartar\\Ncausa cardíaca)","guid":"BipDGP3_yEm2PxdVl1Pwyw","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"284","text":"5️⃣ Neuroimagen (TAC urgente\\No MRI protocolizado)","guid":"dg2GkLARBeAsfJjGlm3UmQ","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"284","text":"6️⃣ EEG (según\\Ncontexto clínico)","guid":"sSSDx7C6IVVBRIdk-H9taw","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"284","text":"7️⃣ Punción lumbar (solo si sospecha\\Nde meningitis/hemorragia)","guid":"pFr5qq6Cv09JXitdiWLrTA","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"284","text":"🔹 Decisiones clave → Confirmación\\Ndiagnóstica, identificación de causa,\\Ninicio de tratamiento","guid":"wiUXIXR1k0WcbzyZyc4iug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"293","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial\\Nde crisis epiléptica","guid":"HVV3WYfk4LJKMbt78aHaxA","children":[{"id":"294","parent":"293","text":"1. Diagnóstico diferencial\\Nprincipal en adultos","guid":"T7dhgDf3wOH5v-da69v5Eg","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"▪ Síncope convulsivo → Movimientos\\Ntónicos o clónicos breves (≤20 seg) tras\\Npérdida de conciencia","guid":"TI9io8iSPgmELAXkKvyYzw","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"294","text":"▪ Accidente isquémico transitorio (AIT)\\N→ Déficits neurológicos transitorios\\Nsin postictal evidente","guid":"XGBlDVjaj1vEEfGr_vvQHw","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"294","text":"▪ Migraña → Aura con progresión en 5-10\\Nmin, sin pérdida de conciencia","guid":"-S18HBNyMEfoWN541G6bAw","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"294","text":"▪ Ataques de pánico / ansiedad →\\NSíntomas subjetivos intensos sin\\Ncorrelato motor típico","guid":"QdPkV88NxumSnhy5cZzLGA","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"294","text":"▪ Crisis psicógenas no epilépticas →\\NMovimientos no estereotipados,\\Nresistencia a apertura ocular","guid":"twQi8cTok_iLjTJMZYemLQ","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"294","text":"▪ Amnesia global transitoria →\\NPérdida repentina de memoria sin\\Notros déficits neurológicos","guid":"zZJgJrIFCMCmuqmiXL8pQg","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"294","text":"▪ Narcolepsia con cataplejia →\\NEpisodios de debilidad muscular sin\\Nactividad epileptiforme en EEG","guid":"1x4RBuyC4UAGBpYQ-A9Mmw","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"294","text":"▪ Trastornos del movimiento\\Nparoxísticos → Distonías\\Nepisódicas, mioclonías no\\Nepilépticas","guid":"-rMGzMVW1zVhD6Gi9FgyaA","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"294","text":"🔹 Eventos durante el sueño →\\NDiferencial con parasomnias REM/no\\NREM, parálisis del sueño","guid":"B0thFwOIIchRK0Sxs5tQAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"304","parent":"293","text":"2. Manejo\\Ntemprano\\Npost-crisis","guid":"L8TciOp9ICXKSDwnrd270Q","children":[{"id":"305","parent":"304","text":"▪ La mayoría de las crisis remiten en\\N<2 min → No se requiere\\Nbenzodiacepinas de inmediato","guid":"-F7sVidUqVAd11FdQJPxrw","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"304","text":"▪ Se asegura acceso IV en\\Nurgencias para administrar\\Nfármacos si la crisis persiste","guid":"eDVYanHl69UFk5TfpWnyCg","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"304","text":"▪ Identificar y tratar\\Ncausas subyacentes","guid":"-mwY68CWrovDToBn0-1gkw","children":[{"id":"308","parent":"307","text":"• Hipoglucemia →\\NTiamina + dextrosa IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"307","text":"• Hiponatremia severa → Corregir\\Nlentamente para evitar mielinolisis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"310","parent":"304","text":"▪ Estado epiléptico (>5-10 min sin\\Nrecuperación de conciencia) → Manejo\\Nespecífico con algoritmo","guid":"WVx4hJZ5Uw5AqQ94NQopIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"293","text":"3. Inicio de\\Ntratamiento\\Nantiepiléptico","guid":"xqtI5FpPAZ2ryQi47Bxm1A","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"3.1. Crisis\\Nsintomática\\Naguda","guid":"0ij5y70PDl9GnBFKOsIfyQ","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"▪ Generalmente no\\Nprogresan a epilepsia","guid":"Fnqp9Q_TTVsiGgzhxdrLOg","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"▪ Manejo depende de la gravedad\\Ndel cuadro subyacente","guid":"1tqljT-Lsi06RiY66p9JbA","children":[{"id":"315","parent":"314","text":"• TEC, ACV agudo, meningitis,\\Nencefalopatía anóxica → Uso temporal\\Nde fármacos antiepilépticos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"316","parent":"314","text":"• Crisis metabólicas (hiponatremia,\\Nhipoglucemia) → Bajo riesgo de epilepsia,\\Npero alto riesgo de recurrencia aguda","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"317","parent":"312","text":"🔹 Fármacos en pacientes críticos\\N→ Levetiracetam,\\Nfosfenitoína/fenitoína, ácido\\Nvalproico","guid":"W1wWbg5REcOab8F9CxDfWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"318","parent":"311","text":"3.2. Primera crisis\\Nno provocada","guid":"BHha7p0XnsbqO78yqnQXxg","children":[{"id":"319","parent":"318","text":"▪ Mayor riesgo de\\Nrecurrencia → Epilepsia","guid":"dd1po_cntbXvAgti_NnxMg","children":[]},{"id":"320","parent":"318","text":"▪ Decisión individualizada → Basada en\\Nhistoria, EEG, neuroimagen","guid":"Xm-o8pACVhq9QB1NjqIJaw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"321","parent":"293","text":"4. Criterios de\\Nhospitalización","guid":"4mKHBJSjH9b_0Kxs5anE_w","children":[{"id":"322","parent":"321","text":"▪ Estado postictal\\Nprolongado","guid":"GndPXXEbV2Iv0hX8lIC-4w","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"321","text":"▪ Recuperación\\Nincompleta","guid":"6LWQdAQGApGN5v3zqYDL9A","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"321","text":"▪ Lesión traumática\\Ngrave asociada","guid":"yMfWtZ26k65-x2_U7qYdOQ","children":[]},{"id":"325","parent":"321","text":"▪ Estado epiléptico","guid":"zo55ujLEw2fuFV4OHnbAJA","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"321","text":"▪ Enfermedad neurológica\\No sistémica aguda","guid":"nUQY_qd7gQ70mTg0MYSk9g","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"321","text":"▪ Dificultad de acceso a\\Nseguimiento ambulatorio","guid":"skx7NGdXLw-b3nj54dcKdw","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"321","text":"🔹 Pacientes sin hallazgos graves\\Npueden ser dados de alta con\\Nseguimiento estrecho","guid":"Msb05sdIHFUrliMkiUzNjA","children":[]}]},{"id":"329","parent":"293","text":"5. Derivación a\\Nneurología","guid":"s7YmMT1tB2w4E4tfRs3Sbg","children":[{"id":"330","parent":"329","text":"▪ Primera crisis sin\\Ncausa obvia","guid":"tdBhzlL9_nXDZr9lHEYIbQ","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"329","text":"▪ Crisis focal con sospecha\\Nde lesión estructural","guid":"F15BaQ99ooOB4UPfIXvhBg","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"329","text":"▪ EEG o neuroimagen con\\Nhallazgos sugestivos de epilepsia","guid":"i-9yDQCDlbnOjpywDM33zQ","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"329","text":"▪ Necesidad de\\Nestratificación de riesgo","guid":"hBlMRq8xb9Mzryi95Jh5Xg","children":[]},{"id":"334","parent":"329","text":"🔹 Clínicas de primera crisis → Hasta\\N50% de los pacientes tienen eventos\\Nprevios no reconocidos","guid":"KON1Qswgxie7e_hfrkBluQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"335","parent":"293","text":"6. Educación\\Ndel paciente","guid":"vrxxMuhmoBIx-YJkicx-OA","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"6.1.\\NPrecauciones\\Ngenerales","guid":"iXBC5F17Eh85BlCtHnXADA","children":[{"id":"337","parent":"336","text":"▪ Evitar factores desencadenantes\\N→ Privación de sueño, alcohol,\\Nfármacos de riesgo","guid":"bIAwLW7KMENxf1_KGHGEEQ","children":[]},{"id":"338","parent":"336","text":"▪ Evitar actividades peligrosas → Natación\\Nsin supervisión, baños de inmersión,\\Nalturas, maquinaria pesada","guid":"_2Q4nYyup1aqCkiBKDhFaw","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"336","text":"▪ Alto riesgo de ahogamiento →\\NMejor duchas que baños","guid":"13S71LEN_bPrMRPYDXSkcQ","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"336","text":"🔹 Epilepsia asociada a mayor\\Nriesgo de mortalidad por\\Naccidentes, suicidio y SUDEP","guid":"3TkMl_EbM3pecxCoKFGrYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"341","parent":"335","text":"6.2. Restricciones\\Npara conducir","guid":"tPt1K0yCzAYFHV0pMPMDGg","children":[{"id":"342","parent":"341","text":"▪ Normativa\\Nvariable según\\Npaís","guid":"7eYkRCocqnr9Y6Mj6A3vgA","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"341","text":"▪ Abstinencia obligatoria tras crisis\\Ncon pérdida de conciencia","guid":"C0KnIoa0Yu_gcPve_HAjYg","children":[]},{"id":"344","parent":"341","text":"▪ Médico debe informar sobre\\Nrestricción de conducción al paciente","guid":"4a36rL5l5REzIp_UBa9aKg","children":[]},{"id":"345","parent":"341","text":"🔹 Revisión en consulta → Solo 64% de\\Npacientes reciben consejería sobre\\Nconducción en urgencias","guid":"uk-ug8YodpHFNyOTfeJy5Q","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":345,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"UTD. Evaluación y manejo de la primera convulsión en adulto-2025","id":"map_885","resolved_references":[]}